  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Whereas pruritus is a major symptom in bullous pemphigoid, its characteristics and its impact
      on quality of life have been little studied.

      The objective of this study is to learn more about pruritus characteristics of patients with
      bullous pemphigoid, and in consequence to better understand the pathophysiology of pruritus,
      and then to better treat pruritus in this condition.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
