    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  adult

          -  pruriginous bullous pemphigoid lately diagnosed.

          -  Without PB treatment

          -  MMS (Mini Mental State Examination) ≥ 21

          -  In hospitalization or consultation

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  pregnant woman

          -  nursing women
      </textblock>
